---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout
  title="About - AB Brothers Construction"
  description="AB Brothers Construction is a licensed and insured, family-owned residential general contractor based in Pittsburgh's South Hills with decades of combined experience."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-primary py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">About Us</p>
      <h1 class="text-primary-foreground max-w-2xl">Quality You Can Count On</h1>
      <p class="text-primary-foreground/70 mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg">
        Licensed, insured, and built on referrals since day one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-5">
            AB Brothers Construction is a licensed and insured, family-owned residential general contractor based in Pittsburgh's South Hills. With decades of combined experience, we are committed to providing exceptional craftsmanship and service on every project, no matter the size or scope.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-5">
            We believe that quality work starts with qualified professionals. Our team includes master tradesmen: plumbers, electricians, tilers, and more, who uphold the highest standards of excellence. Each team member is thoroughly vetted, ensuring that you receive superior service from skilled experts.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            When you choose AB Brothers, you're partnering with a team that values professionalism and efficiency. We strive to make every project a stress-free experience for you. Our success is measured by your satisfaction, which is why we take pride in a business built largely on referrals and repeat clients.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="/images/untitled-design-56.png"
            alt="AB Brothers Construction team at work"
            class="w-full rounded-md mb-6"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div class="bg-muted rounded-md p-5">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary font-[family-name:var(--font-display)]">12+</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider">Years</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-muted rounded-md p-5">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary font-[family-name:var(--font-display)]">100+</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider">Projects</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-muted rounded-md p-5">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary font-[family-name:var(--font-display)]">5.0</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider">Rating</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="bg-muted py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Our Standards</p>
        <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-accent rounded-full mb-5"></div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Premium Materials</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We carefully select the products we use, ensuring they are of the highest quality and suited for each project's specific needs. Top-of-the-line building supplies may cost a little more upfront, but our work lasts longer, saving you time and money while increasing your home's value.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-accent rounded-full mb-5"></div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Decades of Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Our team brings decades of hands-on experience in the field, allowing us to handle a wide range of projects with precision and skill. We've seen it all, from straightforward bathroom updates to full-home renovations of 1950s builds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-accent rounded-full mb-5"></div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Personalized Service</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We treat every client with the same dedication, providing tailored solutions that meet and exceed expectations. Andrew and Bob work closely with each customer during the planning process, and Bob manages day-to-day project oversight.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meet the Team -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">The Owners</p>
        <h2>Meet Andy & Bob</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white border border-border rounded-md p-8 text-center">
          <div class="border-t-2 border-accent -mt-8 mx-auto w-16 mb-6"></div>
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-primary text-2xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-display)]">AH</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Andy Hovanec</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mt-1 mb-4">Co-Owner</p>
          <a href="tel:4128551849" class="text-accent font-medium text-sm">(412) 855-1849</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-border rounded-md p-8 text-center">
          <div class="border-t-2 border-accent -mt-8 mx-auto w-16 mb-6"></div>
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-primary text-2xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-display)]">BK</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Bob Krapp</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mt-1 mb-4">Co-Owner &amp; Project Manager</p>
          <a href="tel:4126208821" class="text-accent font-medium text-sm">(412) 620-8821</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mt-10 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Andrew and Bob work closely with each customer during the planning process. Bob is the project manager and primary point of contact for the duration of every job. Most of the work is done in-house, with a small group of trusted, licensed tradesmen handling electrical, drywall finishing, and HVAC.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-primary py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-primary-foreground mb-4">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-primary-foreground/70 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8">
        We'd love to hear about your project. Contact us for a free in-home consultation.
      </p>
      <a href={`${base}/contact`} class="inline-block bg-accent text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-accent/90">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
